Package: plexus
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Tool for connecting applications via NAT
 The 'plexus' utility provides ability to connect network
 applications based on UDP protocol via NAT.

